* 1. Apa Itu Python? *

A. Kenapa Belajar Python?
  - Mudah Dimengerti
  - Gratis
  - Dynamic
  - Multi Platform :  - Web Development
                      - Mobile Apps
                      - Desktop Apps
  - Lagi Hype :  - Data Science
                  - Robotics
                  - Machine Learning
                  - Data Analysis
                  - Artificial Intelligent

B. Kok bisa Python populer?
            - Bahasanya Simple bila dibandingkan dengan C++ & Java

C. Siapa penemu/pembuat bahasa Python?
    Pencipta : Guido Van Rossum (Programmer) pada tahun 1989
    Pada awalnya bertemu Andrew S. Tenenbaum yang meminta untuk dibuatkan bahasa yang cocok untuk Amoeba (Distributed Operating System Amoeba)

D. Sejarah Perkembangan Python
  1989 -->  Pyhton 1.0 (Jan 1994) Release Pertama
                    1.5 CRNI (Dec 1997) Keyword argument, Complex Number
                    1.6 BeOpen.com  (Sept 2000) GPL-compatible License Python distribution utilities (disutils)
                    2.0 Python Enhancement Proposal (PEP) (Oct 2000) List Comprehensions, Garbage Collection, Python Software Foundation License
                    2.2 (Dec 2001) Types (in C), Class
                    2.5 (Sept 2006) With Statement
                    2.7 (Jul 2010) Final Python 2.x
            Python 3.0 (Dec 2008) ReDesign Multi-Paradigm
                    3.1 (Jun 2009) Ordered Dict, Formal String
                    3.2 (Feb 2011) Stable ABI Argparse
                    3.3 (Sept 2012) virtualenv, Implicit namespace, Flexible string, Python launcher for Windows, OS & IO Exception
                    3.4 (Mar 2014) PIP included, New Modules
                    3.5 (Sept 2015) coroutines, Matrix operator
                    3.6 (Dec 2016) Format string literal, underscore in numeric literal, variable annotations, asynchronous generator and comprehensions
                    3.7 (Jun 2018) Postponed evaluation of type annotations
                    3.8 (Oct 2019) New syntax :=, Positional-only parameters, f-string, Improved moduls
                    3.9 (Oct 2020) Deprecation Warning for 2.7, Dictionary merge & update operators

E. Apa yang dibutuhkan untuk mulai belajar Python?
    1. Python + IDE (Integrated Development Environment, contoh : PyChar.?.)
    2. Python + Interactive Python Shell (I-Python, Spider, Jupiter NoteBook)
    3. Python + Text Editor (Visual Studio Code)
